text: Jinju Stadium (), is a multi-use stadium in Jinju, South Korea It is used mostly for football matches. The stadium was built in 2010 and designed for a capacity of 20,116 spectators. This stadium is different from the old stadium Jinju Civic Stadium. == See also == * Jinju Civic Stadium ==References== ==External links== *Official website *Stadium information Category:Football venues in South Korea Category:Athletics (track and field) venues in South Korea Category:Sports venues in South Gyeongsang Province Category:Jinju
